			<h2>28th Moonst, 256</h2>
			<p>It has been a quite month since Winter arrived but today another body was discovered drained of blood.  This is the first such body since sequestering the other vampires in the switch room.  I hope this is an old body that was recently discovered rather than the prey of a new vampire.  We will have to look more closely at the last few batches of immigrants...</p>
